<title type="html"><![CDATA[Five Nights At Freddy's and SCP-173 Buttons]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4573&amp;p=19146#p19146"><![CDATA[
Now for some indie horror game themed start buttons. To download the buttons, right click and choose to save image.<br /><br />Here's a pack of 6 &quot;Five Nights At Freddy's&quot; start buttons. I apologize for the quality here, it was really difficult finding suitable images to use for them, let alone anything of high quality. I had to make do with what I could find. The middle (hot) button images doesn't show up well on this solid lightly colored background, but it should look better on your taskbar. I think the buttons look best if you set the size somewhere in the 42-50 range.<br /><br /><img src="http://i51.photobucket.com/albums/f395/barguestspirit/Windows%20Start%20Buttons/FNAF%20Freddy%20Start%20Button.png" alt="" /> <img src="http://i51.photobucket.com/albums/f395/barguestspirit/Windows%20Start%20Buttons/FNAF%20Bonnie%20Start%20Button.png" alt="" /> <img src="http://i51.photobucket.com/albums/f395/barguestspirit/Windows%20Start%20Buttons/FNAF%20Chica%20Start%20Button.png" alt="" /> <img src="http://i51.photobucket.com/albums/f395/barguestspirit/Windows%20Start%20Buttons/FNAF%20Foxy%20Start%20Button.png" alt="" /> <img src="http://i51.photobucket.com/albums/f395/barguestspirit/Windows%20Start%20Buttons/FNAF%20Golden%20Freddy%20Start%20Button.png" alt="" /> <img src="http://i51.photobucket.com/albums/f395/barguestspirit/Windows%20Start%20Buttons/FNAF%20Springtrap%20Start%20Button.png" alt="" /><br /><br /><br /><br />Lastly, here's a button featuring SCP-173 from &quot;SCP Containment Breach&quot;. If you're unfamiliar with SCP Containment Breach, check out the main <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/" class="postlink">SCP site</a>, do a little reading, then go to the <a href="http://www.scpcbgame.com/" class="postlink">SCP Containment Breach game site</a> and download the game (it's free, and some good creepy fun). Set the button size according to your preference (Probably best around 42-55).<br /><br /><img src="http://i51.photobucket.com/albums/f395/barguestspirit/Windows%20Start%20Buttons/SCP%20173%20Start%20Button.png" alt="" /><br /><br />That's it, enjoy! <img src="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/images/smilies/icon_e_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" /><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=10094">Barguestspirit</a> â€” Mon Apr 27, 2015 6:44 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
